{"level":"info","message":"Main 微信文章抓取成功，注入内容","textLen":6600,"timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:58:59.481Z","title":"Claude Code 十个最值得装的 Skills：不是越多越能打，是这 10 个最能打！！"}
{"input":{"category":"claude-code","content":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9OOV_phsQacXQjeUF1jVug\n\n标题：Claude Code 十个最值得装的 Skills\n\n核心观点：Claude Code 的上限不只是模型决定的，更是你给它配了哪一组 skills 决定的。\n\n10 个推荐 Skills（含安装命令）：\n\n1. agent-browser（最优先）\n   npx skills add vercel-labs/agent-browser@agent-browser -g -y\n   → 让 Claude Code 操控浏览器，执行网页任务，从 coding assistant 变成真正的 agent\n\n2. find-skills\n   npx skills add vercel-labs/skills@find-skills -g -y\n   → skills 生态搜索入口，避免重复造轮子\n\n3. summarize\n   npx skills add steipete/clawdis@summarize -g -y\n   → 压缩长网页/文档/播客/会议记录，提炼信息\n\n4. skill-creator\n   npx skills add anthropics/skills@skill-creator -g -y\n   → 把自己的高频工作流沉淀成可复用 skill\n\n5. tmux\n   npx skills add steipete/clawdis@tmux -g -y\n   → 控制持久终端会话，适合长任务/远程/并行任务\n\n6. testing / e2e / playwright\n   npx skills add anthropics/skills@webapp-testing -g -y\n   → 让测试代码更稳定、结构更专业\n\n7. docs / readme / api-docs\n   npx skills add googleworkspace/cli@gws-docs -g -y\n   → 给代码补文档，结构化输出\n\n8. refactor / review / best-practices\n   npx skills add supercent-io/skills-template@code-refactoring -g -y\n   → 从\"能用\"推向\"资深工程师级别\"的代码质量\n\n9. git-workflow / changelog / release\n   npx skills add supercent-io/skills-template@changelog-maintenance -g -y\n   → 自动化 commit message、changelog、release note\n\n10. research / web-search（推荐 Tavily）\n    npx skills add tavily-ai/skills@research -g -y\n    → 让 Claude Code 变成调研助理：搜、读、摘、比\n\n优先级梯队：\n- 第一梯队：agent-browser、summarize、find-skills\n- 第二梯队：skill-creator、tmux、testing/docs/refactor 类","note":"Skills 生态完整指南，有具体安装命令，下次 Claude Code 会话可直接按梯队逐步安装配置"},"level":"info","message":"Main 调用工具","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:59:17.778Z","tool":"queue_knowledge"}
